about.description:
Main purpose of this library to support amazon s3 api, but other services
should work (may be with minor fixes). For now it has been tested only for
upload/download api for s3. It has been reported that SQS and Dynamo
services also work.
about.summary: Async client for aws services using botocore and aiohttp

about.description:
Main purpose of this library to support amazon s3 api, but other services
should work (may be with minor fixes). For now it has been tested only for

services also work.

name: aiobotocore
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "aiobotocore" %}
{% set version = "2.11.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6dd7352248e3523019c5a54a395d2b1c31080697fc80a9ad2672de4eec8c7abd

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.8
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.8
    - aiohttp >=3.7.4.post0,<4.0.0
    - aioitertools >=0.5.1,<1.0.0
    - botocore >=1.33.2,<1.34.35
    - wrapt >=1.10.10,<2.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - aiobotocore
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/aio-libs/aiobotocore
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Async client for aws services using botocore and aiohttp
  description: |
    Main purpose of this library to support amazon s3 api, but other services
    should work (may be with minor fixes). For now it has been tested only for
    upload/download api for s3. It has been reported that SQS and Dynamo
    services also work.
  doc_url: http://aiobotocore.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/aio-libs/aiobotocore

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nehaljwani
